        crm:P3_has_note               "Panel painting attributed to Raffaello Sanzio da Urbino, depicting Pope Leo X flanked by two cardinals. The work is currently held at the Galleria degli Uffizi, Florence. It was the subject of a macro X-ray fluorescence (MA-XRF) scanning campaign aimed at studying the painting palette and technique, and contextualising Raffaello's working methods."@en ;
